{"tid":434083,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦用用下會熄左機","createTime":"2017-10-13T02:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T12:01:55.000Z","uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1926513c3b6fa7cbae0bf48663a71034a4abf965","tid":434083,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:58:12.000Z","msg":"我個野壞左呀<br />\n之前部電腦用用下變左極慢<br />\n之嘛就洗左機啦 洗左機之後反而開唔返<br />\n之後清左次塵 拆左個cpu 出黎見到散熱膏乾哂 所有就買左支返黎換<br />\n咁就開得返機<br />\n但係而家用用下就會自己熄 之前用到夜晚先熄<br />\n而家用兩個鐘就熄 熄完開返都用唔耐<br />\n究竟咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18dd30fb4177b5ed76cdf7b70482b24824d061c","tid":434083,"uid":81703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"過熱"},{"pid":"d1526f041a2c1681d038a7f5753a0f48f56661fe","tid":434083,"uid":46984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"咁點算好 應該換啲咩野佢"},{"pid":"f79843c407c9bcd17bb9fbd98ae11aeed9c8bd0b","tid":434083,"uid":81703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:18:31.000Z","msg":"睇睇裝正個散熱未"},{"pid":"978a7d802ae81e31897b5e9baaf337a359965a18","tid":434083,"uid":81703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"用隻手輕輕摩把風扇是否停?"},{"pid":"c57dcc1c2be27da69dd3d25df982e568e0b332d8","tid":434083,"uid":108450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"同問 用用下息機等好耐先開得返。即刻開既話個mon唔會著。低板燈有著所有風扇有轉。 但係有時低板燈都唔會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebc080840174dddb2cb9b8c3f7da4ce5562e9f0","tid":434083,"uid":137487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b3ba85ad06b064c2355c6537a3f6289cf89715","t